rawContent:
Imagine any other job from plumbing to medicine where you just don't see eye to eye with a coworker and just stop producing.. Where in the world is that acceptable except in Congress. 

The rest of us have to agree to disagree and work together fix the pipe or patjent.

Maybe model for the country how to get shit done?

rawContent:
A decent man, @MJGerson RIP. 

He told me a great story about getting home & settling in late one night & getting a late night call from Bono asking to meet up at a hotel bar. 

Of course he got dressed & “hung out” till the early morning.  
Peace be upon you old friend.
renderedContent:
A decent man, @MJGerson RIP. 

He told me a great story about getting home & settling in late one night & getting a late night call from Bono asking to meet up at a hotel bar. 

Of course he got dressed & “hung out” till the early morning.  
Peace be upon you old friend.
